{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/6043", "repo": "rails", "body": "Yes, I am translating guides into Traditional Chinese.\r\n\r\nWhenever I want to translate something like `h3. \u524d\u60c5\u63d0\u8981`, it goes wrong in what I mentioned.\r\nA simple way to solve this problem is to specify an explicit ID like `h3(#this-guide-assumes). \u524d\u60c5\u63d0\u8981`, but it's getting annoying when I have to write every headers like this.\r\n\r\nThat's why I choose to use MD5 approach.=)", "_id": {"$oid": "52380fbfbd3543c15100d581"}, "issue_id": 6043, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/5403876", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6043#issuecomment-5403876", "updated_at": "2012-04-29T09:58:57Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tonytonyjan/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tonytonyjan/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tonytonyjan/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tonytonyjan/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/tonytonyjan", "login": "tonytonyjan", "gravatar_id": "2a01ae9942939ee2b3954a6727d2bb92", "html_url": "https://github.com/tonytonyjan", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tonytonyjan/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tonytonyjan/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tonytonyjan/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/2a01ae9942939ee2b3954a6727d2bb92?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F52f939eab7604225e246d02aa4651605.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tonytonyjan/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 809410, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/tonytonyjan/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2012-04-29T09:58:20Z", "id": 5403876, "owner": "rails"}
